<p>Tame pigs and wild boars</p>
<p>Escape to a new frontier</p>
<p>Away from safety</p>
<hr>
<p>Loud trumpets above</p>
<p>The earth cracks beneath my feet</p>
<p>Hearing angel calls</p>
<hr>
<p>Feast on loving death</p>
<p>The rot consumes living flesh</p>
<p>Maggots destroy sustenance</p>
<hr>
<p>Tower of babel</p>
<p>Reach towards beloved futures</p>
<p>We all vainly fall down</p>
<hr>
<p>Language disperse</p>
<p>Hear a mother weep loudly</p>
<p>Seeking is fruitless</p>
<hr>
<p>I hear its loud cries</p>
<p>Begging for loud forgiveness</p>
<p>I do not reach out</p>
<hr>
<p>Eat my uselessness</p>
<p>Consume my dull sacrifice</p>
<p>Come undone by teeth</p>